data.description: This spacious four-bedroom two bathroom Pottsboro home is ready for it’s new owners. With an open concept and two spacious living areas it is perfect for entertaining or just enjoying time with your family. The neighborhood is great for evening walks. The large backyard has ample room for any activity and is a blank canvas. There is so much potential. This home is priced to sell and will not last long. Come, see it today!
